{NORTH opens 1NT with 15 points and a balanced hand.

SOUTH, with 9 points, cannot bid game herself, but she can invite NORTH to bid game if he 
has the maximum 17 point opener. So she responds 2NT.

NORTH doesn't have maximum, he has minimum, so he passes.}

